## traceId 传递

```typescript
// ❌ BAD — traceId 丢失
async function handler(req, res) {
  const result = await searchUseCase.execute(req.body);
  res.json(result);
}

// ✅ GOOD — 中间件注入 + 全链路透传
async function handler(req: Request, res: Response) {
  const traceId = req.headers['x-trace-id'] ?? generateTraceId();
  res.setHeader('x-trace-id', traceId);
  const result = await searchUseCase.execute(req.body, { traceId });
  res.json(result);
}
```

- HTTP 响应头回传 `x-trace-id`
- 异步任务（Celery）将 traceId 写入 task payload
- GraphQL Context 注入 `{ traceId, logger }`

