## Langfuse 埋点

```typescript
// ❌ BAD — 无埋点、无 token 统计
const response = await llm.invoke(prompt);

// ✅ GOOD
const span = langfuse.trace({ id: traceId, name: 'knowledge-search' });
const generation = span.generation({
  name: 'embed-query',
  model: embedModel,
  input: redactSensitive(input.query),
});
try {
  const response = await llm.invoke(prompt, { callbacks: [langfuseHandler] });
  generation.end({
    output: redactSensitive(response.content),
    usage: { input: response.usage?.promptTokens, output: response.usage?.completionTokens },
  });
  return response;
} catch (err) {
  generation.end({ level: 'ERROR', statusMessage: String(err) });
  throw err;
}
```

- Prompt / Completion 入库前调用 `redactSensitive()`
- 记录 model 名称、latency、token 用量、错误状态

